room_title: Escape room "Bank Heist" by Countdown Games in Lexington
room_description:
Every Sunday at midnight, the bank security system resets for one hour. Your friend who owns a toy store has been planning a bank heist and was caught. He left you some notes and clues to pull it off yourself with one problem: the key to the bank is in the vault.
You have to get into the bank, into the vault, and then pick the right safety deposit box before the security system and the police catch you red handed.
